data.description: Grandview Island is the best kept secret in Hampton Roads! Ever dream of jumping on your boat or watercraft from your private dock, right in your own backyard? Enjoy the warm breezes by land as you cruise through this golf-cart friendly neighborhood. Just a short walk down the street, you can explore the beautiful nature preserve and pristine beach year-round. Three beautiful bedroom suites, open floor plan, sun and water view from almost every room and 200 ft. of bulkhead/deep water access… something special for everyone! Modern design boasts several rooms that can be multi-purposed to fit your wants/needs. Electric heated floor in primary shower suite. Remote controlled motorized blackout shades. Elegant 8' x 4'-foot Brazilian natural quartzite island with seating for 8 plus. White high gloss, modern kitchen cabinets with easy pull-out drawers with lighting. Custom built-in wet bar. Modern deep soaking tub with expansive dressing room. Must See!
